author: Staff report
title: Chambersburg football coach Mark Saunders resigns after 0-5 start
text:
Chambersburg football coach Mark Saunders resigns after 0-5 start Staff report Posted: 10/09/2015 10:44:44 AM EDT Chambersburg football coach Mark Saunders, pictured in 2014, has resigned. (File - Public Opinion) 
Chambersburg Athletic Director Jeremy Flores announced that Trojan football coach Mark Saunders resigned from his position this morning. The team has been notified. 
Assistant coach Scott Mitchell has been named the interim coach for the remainder of the season. 
Chambersburg, which is 0-5, plays its homecoming game tonight at Trojan Stadium, against Mifflin County (0-5).
